-to-the-greatest-songwriter-of-his-generation-shane-macgowan-after-storied-friendship-3551421">尼克·凯夫（Nick Cave）向他的密友致敬</a>，他将麦克高恩（MacGowan）描述为“他这一代的最伟大的词曲作者”，然后在他们死后向麦克高恩（Macgowan）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">辛纳德·奥康纳（SinéadO&#39;Connor）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-pens-heartfelt-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-and-sinead-oconnor-3552218">致敬</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">皮特·多尔蒂（Pete Doherty）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-doherty-hails-bulletproof-shane-macgowan-as-one-of-the-best-lyricists-of-the-last-30-or-40-years-3552035">回应了这种情绪</a>，记得他是“过去30或40年”中最好的作词家之一，而布鲁斯·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">斯普林斯汀（Bruce Springsteen）</a>则<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-calls-shane-macgowan-one-of-my-all-time-favourite-writers-in-touching-tribute-3552221">写了自己的致敬</a>，形容麦克高恩（Macgowan）是“我一直以来最喜欢的作家之一”。</p><p>同时，U2支付了音乐敬意，U2在拉斯维加斯球场<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-u2-play-a-rainy-night-in-soho-in-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-3552402">上表演了“在Soho”的“雨天之夜”的封面</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-glen-hansard-friends-cover-the-pogues-a-rainy-night-in-soho-in-tribute-to-shane-macgowan-3553217">格伦·汉萨德（Glen Hansard）还带领一群爱尔兰音乐家</a>以这首歌的版本。</p><p>他去世后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-are-rallying-to-get-the-pogues-fairytale-of-new-york-to-christmas-number-one-after-death-of-shane-macgowan-3551355">球迷们开始集会，将“纽约的童话”成为圣诞节的第一名</a>- <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pogues-fairytale-of-new-york-re-enters-top-40-following-shane-macgowans-death-3552257">自从重新进入前40名以来</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shane-macgowans-cause-of-death-revealed-as-wife-honours-the-blessings-he-brought-3553680">Shane MacGowan后的死因被揭示为妻子荣誉“他带来的祝福”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
